title: Catalyst - Book One: You Are The Light
description:
This is the first book in a trilogy. If you're a fan of comic books, dark fantasy set in a real world environment, or if you're just bored as shit, you may be interested in giving this tale a look. It's listed on Amazon Books for $2.99. If you read/enjoy it you'll find a link at the end of the novel to its Amazon page. If you wanna drop $2.99 on it, cool. If you enjoyed it and don't wanna pay me shit, that's cool too. Whatever the case may be, I hope you enjoy this tale I've penned.

This torrent contains the ebook as a mobi and PDF file.

Happy reading.

Adam Wolf

Peeeeeeeeeeeeeeeace!
